{"tid":42490,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"新手跑步jj有野問","createTime":"2016-12-16T16:58:52.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-22T17:59:54.000Z","uid":3172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"14a88dbceef1cb1c18a932b2f1d50b2b00ad2873","tid":42490,"uid":3172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T16:58:52.000Z","msg":"各位冬天跑步個陣係點保暖嫁?<br />\n<br />\n小弟今日跑5k都好似熱唔起個人咁  就算流汗個人都係凍<br />\n<br />\n同埋呢  呼吸d冷空氣好辛苦  氣管心口都好凍咁  咁樣係咪正常嫁？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n跑齡9個月"},{"pid":"71d2d8c91f09c4afe288f73396ec9bcae802af50","tid":42490,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T17:00:00.000Z","msg":"有人會著黑絲<br />\n利申：外行"},{"pid":"9ca6da2b3a6a6ab877c7d7c7b1cf89f2196e5ba8","tid":42490,"uid":12037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T17:00:15.000Z","msg":"著tight"},{"pid":"29acd278b705a7380e1b09ee41cd4d121e319a54","tid":42490,"uid":3172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T17:01:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有人會著黑絲<br />\n利申：外行</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n著左heattech都熱唔起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fba6b7a6e822c29e96584d0e6095e707d1986b64","tid":42490,"uid":3172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T17:01:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>著tight</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n褲黎？"},{"pid":"f1eed9541a34d76aaa4c77c9db8fa5fa3ddfa471","tid":42490,"uid":3963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T17:03:40.000Z","msg":"上身著一件背心一件短袖加多一件長袖(全部都係dry fit) 下身著條長嘅緊身褲 咁其實已經夠暖"},{"pid":"f63de1eee8ef93a89f1d333609904569707046be","tid":42490,"uid":3963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T17:04:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上身著一件背心一件短袖加多一件長袖(全部都係dry fit) 下身著條<span style=\"color: red;\">長嘅緊身褲</span>咁其實已經夠暖</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n姐係長tight"},{"pid":"2b6dd1d43052b63279b8d6ce7d967e125722bc95","tid":42490,"uid":49716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T17:06:32.000Z","msg":"有無拉筋先跑"},{"pid":"b952716c75fc2eb243365ba607a12b4e985bd533","tid":42490,"uid":3172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T17:07:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>上身著一件背心一件短袖加多一件長袖(全部都係dry fit) 下身著條<span style=\"color: red;\">長嘅緊身褲</span>咁其實已經夠暖</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n姐係長tight</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nthanks  巴打"},{"pid":"dbd5ac1cce8eb181a5cb25d149ef382d166fb256","tid":42490,"uid":3172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T17:08:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無拉筋先跑</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n習慣跑完拉   咁樣得唔得嫁？   因為我未跑拉試過抽筋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4307b0341412a06eae325bc84b931dc35a0c67a3","tid":42490,"uid":66740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T18:03:57.000Z","msg":"強度唔夠，個心泵唔夠血，血液循環唔夠快，所以凍，結論：跑快d"},{"pid":"b934285035c986795d3f9c8f7082a27b9a3c47ca","tid":42490,"uid":49716,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T18:08:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有無拉筋先跑</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n習慣跑完拉   咁樣得唔得嫁？   因為我未跑拉試過抽筋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n拉左先跑會好啲，正常係跑之前拉鬆跑完再做cool down<br />\n同埋拉左筋慢跑一陣再加速個人會熱好多<br />\n利申：我自己係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2d620a190a939134d0472929f0301a302e82491","tid":42490,"uid":60520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T18:14:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有無拉筋先跑</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n習慣跑完拉   咁樣得唔得嫁？   因為我未跑拉試過抽筋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n拉左先跑會好啲，正常係跑之前拉鬆跑完再做cool down<br />\n同埋拉左筋慢跑一陣再加速個人會熱好多<br />\n利申：我自己係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n輕鬆慢跑令到個人熱左，<br />\n然後拉筋再先真正開始跑<br />\n跑完再做cool down <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99fde8cd103eb3f51d97712781dce69996eb84ce","tid":42490,"uid":3172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T19:26:19.000Z","msg":"thanks  各位指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9bfc3c9ddae7c3c09385eb3b62581a5ba0694df","tid":42490,"uid":51108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T19:31:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有人會著黑絲<br />\n利申：外行</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n著左heattech都熱唔起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nheattech唔放風，梗係凍啦<br />\n我而家通常跟dcrainmaker個clothing guide,好凖，值得參考<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.dcrainmaker.com/2012/01/what-i-wear-cold-weather-running.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dcrainmaker.com%2F2012%2F01%2Fwhat-i-wear-cold-weather-running.html&d=bdfRKPyRx1hzTk0oy89QxksIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=5536cfdc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.dcrainmaker.com/2012/01/what-i-wear-cold-weather-running.html</a>"},{"pid":"d0ed83e7f154b275bd59c19683f7348887ff23f2","tid":42490,"uid":6869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T09:22:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e7a1391f4bba1d01b7a12ab4f98c65047850c5a6","tid":42490,"uid":65160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T11:57:58.000Z","msg":"劇烈出汗時 除衫<br />\n緩跑休閒時 著番<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 利申 鳩up"},{"pid":"635a414bb4124a63fce6548c1e69844e6c575298","tid":42490,"uid":43060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T12:00:47.000Z","msg":"口吸氣 用條脷頂住上顎 吸個d冷空氣冇咁易令你個喉嚨同口腔乾"},{"pid":"ca26ecce926d694833529894a07b7b4f866a2893","tid":42490,"uid":5244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,